name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Walmart Split - A part of Splitzy

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps using Walmart Split more easily. Please login in our website before using this extension.
How to use this extension:
Go to the Walmart orders page and signin.

Open the order you want to add to splitwise

Open this extension and click on the button below and your order items will be ready for you
